description:
Captive Minecraft is a 1.10 vanilla custom map where the goal is to grow the boundaries by completing achievements. This allows you to further explore the world and find what you need to complete the victory monument.

This map is available from the Farlanders at:
http://thefarlanders.com/captiveminecraftiv/
